# Portfolio Website

React 19 + TypeScript (strict) portfolio at https://nickhs.dev. Vite build, Cloudflare Pages deploy.

## Before committing

1. `nvm use` then `yarn lint:fix`
2. `yarn test` (and `yarn test:e2e` if UI changed)
3. Pre-commit hooks run ESLint, Stylelint, Prettier, and `tsc --noEmit` on staged files

## Adding features

1. Component in `src/components/ComponentName/`
2. CSS in `src/styles/ComponentName/ComponentName.css`
3. Types in `src/types/*.types.ts`
4. Content in `src/data/` when applicable
5. Wire up in `App.tsx` or parent; add section `id` for navbar scroll targets

## Key libraries

- `react-animate-on-scroll` — scroll animations (`animateOnce` on sections)
- `animate.css` — animation classes
- `swiper` — carousels
- `react-inlinesvg` — inline SVG manipulation

## Do not

- Edit `CHANGELOG.md` manually (semantic-release)
- Use Tailwind or CSS-in-JS
- Use class components (except `ErrorBoundary`)
